==English==

===Etymology===
From [[w:Walter H. Schottky|Walter H. Schottky]] German physicist

===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[Schottky]] [[anomaly]]|Schottky anomalies}}

#{{physics}} A [[variation]] in the [[heat capacity]] of a solid at low temperatures which arises from the [[thermal]] [[population]] of [[discrete]] [[energy level]]s as the temperature is raised

